textBox.richText: At Exhibitor LIVE 2016, we are doing something new, different, and exciting. We have teamed up with SoftSpace, combining our 30’ x 25’ spaces to make a 30 x 50 space where we will showcase our complimentary skillsets in building one beautiful exhibit bringing life to the words “Let’s Build Something Together..” It’s not only an invitation to you to participate but a demonstration of how it can be done.. We look forward to seeing you in Vegas!
